sourcesContent: import axios from "axios"import store from "./store"export default () => {    return axios.create({        baseURL: "https://auth.scalingo.com/v1/",        header: {            "Authorization": "Bearer " + store.state.token,            "Access-Control-Allow-Origin": "*",            'Access-Control-Allow-Headers': 'Content-Type',            'Content-Type': 'application/json-rpc',            'Accept': 'application/json-rpc'        }    })}
